262
00:10:07,836 --> 00:10:10,204
Spike: We got an image from the
CCTV, it's gone to your phones.

263
00:10:10,271 --> 00:10:11,606
Jules:
No sign of Tobias.

264
00:10:11,673 --> 00:10:12,773
Ed: If Tobias took a
blow to the head,

265
