in the car.

266
00:10:14,175 --> 00:10:14,842
Parker: You heard
three shots, right?

267
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,477
David:
Yeah.

268
00:10:16,545 --> 00:10:17,244
Ed: So one when you land,
and the second hit here...

269
00:10:17,312 --> 00:10:18,212
And then one outside.

